Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:02.41,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}此刻從此開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:05.05,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}試著想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:07.81,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}自己能做到什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:12.59,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}有出乎意料的變故
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:17.71,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}一定能夠越過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:19.84,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}power of dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:23.08,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}一切從0開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.56,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}閃耀著飛向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:30.36,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}light blue wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:33.53,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}下定決心展翅飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:39.94,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}用最美的笑容  出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:45.02,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}現在向未知的世界起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:51.34,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}未來的選擇  做決定的是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:53.74,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}去追逐夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.30,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}也會有想哭的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:02:00.95,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}那是最重要的願望  不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:05.82,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}一定能和明天的你再次相見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:13.07,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}get out of the gate true sky
